ActWild Animal and Plant Protection and Regulation of International and Interprovincial Trade Act
PrecisRegulations Amending the WILD ANIMAL AND PLANT TRADE REGULATIONS by protecting Canadian and foreign species of animals and plants that may be at risk of over-exploitation due to illegal trade, and safeguard Canadian ecosystems from the introduction of species designated as harmful. The amendments will bring Canada's Regulations into alignment with all other Parties to the Convention.
